{"lastModified":1764334824634,"uri":"c::7580644256::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Bahamas, Leeward Islands\n\nCHARTER IN THE BAHAMAS THIS WINTER ABOARD M/Y RISK AND REWARD\n\nMotor Yacht RISK & REWARD is an exquisite and refined yacht celebrated for its streamlined design and exceptional performance on the water. It offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and modern technology, making it a top choice for discerning charter enthusiasts. RISK & REWARD offers diverse outdoor areas, with the sun deck standing out as a captivating entertainment hub, generous aft decks, and a Jacuzzi with a custom-made Sun Lounger, allowing guests to soak up the sun and enjoy stunning views. With the addition of a newly purchased 39′ HCB, water activities will be a once-in-a-lifetime experience.","blueprint":{"name":"RISK & REWARD","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dff7eae0-edcd-11ef-affb-3db9728da06b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dfe9ba10-edcd-11ef-aff9-3db9728da06b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dff293b0-edcd-11ef-affa-3db9728da06b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dfe65eb0-edcd-11ef-aff6-3db9728da06b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dff1a950-edcd-11ef-affa-3db9728da06b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dff68b50-edcd-11ef-affb-3db9728da06b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dff1f770-edcd-11ef-affb-3db9728da06b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca322-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dfe72200-edcd-11ef-aff8-3db9728da06b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::ves